dct_title_s: Rutgers University and routes to stadium
dct_description_sm: location map of Rutgers University showing the vicinity of New Brunswick, New Jersey and routes to the Rutgers Stadium. Inset of stadium and parking lots, athletic fields and golf course. Three drawn illustrations depict the Old Queens building, the Rutgers Stadium and the Rutgers Gymnasium.
